data.description: This is an outstanding opportunity! This 3 bedroom home is ready for you to come in and make your own. Great for entertaining with a huge backyard including a swimming pool and oversized back porch. Large den can be turned into a bedroom, or enjoyed as a second living area. Solar panels included in the price of the home which will significantly lower your energy expenses!
